{
  "stem": "617.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I suppose my mother could have come with us, because she was young.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But because she had a child and another child with her, she was taken.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So there were anywhere from 14 to 40.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were a lot in the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But different people, what they can do different work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that-- and-- and that was the first time we worked, was in Auchswitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't work while in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after about three weeks, we were shipped out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we were shipped out-- it was by train-- to an area where it was forests.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were-- there were tents set up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Black tents.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And for bathrooms, there were latrines, you know, just huge latrines with bars.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Those were the-- and there was-- it was daylight 24 hours a day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The sun would go down, but there it wasn't night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in the mornings, sometimes you would get up, and there was, like, dew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Wet.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everything was wet.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we wouldn't-- you know, that one could hide in the-- on the fields and not be seen, because the-- You know, it-- later-- I didn't know at the time-- we were close to the-- by the Baltic Sea.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the daytime, we used to work in the forest, cutting trees.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Could you imagine?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Girls cutting trees with saws.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then after the trees would fall, we had to cut them into pieces.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then taken back to camp at night, like which was the-- you know, bed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's where we get our food, the little food what we'd get.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
